  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i><u>Main story</u></i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/b923dec21203ec54f5e94441472db1ae.poster.avif?t=1772901968\" width=610 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/b923dec21203ec54f5e94441472db1ae.webm?t=1772901968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/b923dec21203ec54f5e94441472db1ae.mp4?t=1772901968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of a police officer assigned to investigate an earthquake at the renowned \"Santa Margarita\" school at year 2003.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/cc488da7d8c6ecd1538cfebb65af9a0c.poster.avif?t=1772901968\" width=610 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/cc488da7d8c6ecd1538cfebb65af9a0c.webm?t=1772901968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/cc488da7d8c6ecd1538cfebb65af9a0c.mp4?t=1772901968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Your mission is to uncover the truth behind the incident and reveal the school's dark, hidden history. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout your investigation, you'll encounter various paranormal events that defy explanation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/8af3a5c8e515519b779dbbd9fec91821.poster.avif?t=1772901968\" width=610 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/8af3a5c8e515519b779dbbd9fec91821.webm?t=1772901968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/8af3a5c8e515519b779dbbd9fec91821.mp4?t=1772901968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or can you unravel the mysteries? Additionally, you must complete a small list of puzzles that you must discover throughout the first floor of the school.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/37ebb4160c22d1a33b99deeca926b828.poster.avif?t=1772901968\" width=610 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/37ebb4160c22d1a33b99deeca926b828.webm?t=1772901968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/37ebb4160c22d1a33b99deeca926b828.mp4?t=1772901968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>Game features:</strong></i>  </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Duration of 1.5 hours </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploration </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realistic graphics  </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VHS style </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set on Halloween dates </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NORMAL level puzzles </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contains gory material and may be sensitive for some audiences</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>THE GAME WILL BE GETTING MORE CONTENT AS UPDATES GO BY</i></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contact the team: <strong><a href=\"mailto:papus.studio2024@gmail.com\">papus.studio2024@gmail.com</a></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We will be happy to bring you new content and solve problems in future updates!</p>",
